EM<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 con tr\u1ebb kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung ch\u01b0a ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd n\u1ed9i dung xem truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh theo \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1eddi gian m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd th\u00f4ng qua m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u.<\/p>\n<\/div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https:\/\/tongdai-fpt.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/lap-dat-truyen-hinh-fpt-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cantho-fpt.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/lap-dat-truyen-hinh-fpt-2.jpeg 1000w, https:\/\/cantho-fpt.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/lap-dat-truyen-hinh-fpt-2-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/cantho-fpt.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/lap-dat-truyen-hinh-fpt-2-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"TINH NANG GIAM SAT TRE EM P1 - Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh FPT Play\" width=\"1020\" height=\"574\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/-OJiyCBjSOc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p><strong>Video h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng&nbsp;GI\u00c1M S\u00c1T TR\u1eba EM<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:<\/strong>&nbsp;T\u1ea1i m\u1ee5c trang ch\u1ee7 thao t\u00e1c ph\u00edm \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n. D\u00f9ng ph\u00edm \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng xu\u1ed1ng, ch\u1ecdn gi\u1ea3m s\u00e1t tr\u1ebb em,&nbsp;<strong>\u1ea5n OK<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2:<\/strong>&nbsp;Nh\u1eadp m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u (M\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u m\u1eb7c \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 123456). T\u1ea1i m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eaft,&nbsp;<strong>\u1ea5n OK<\/strong>&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eadt l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p><strong>h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng&nbsp;\u0110I\u1ec0U KHI\u1ec2N B\u1eb0NG GI\u1eccNG N\u00d3I<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i t\u1eeb k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn phim truy\u1ec7n, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed9i dung y\u00eau th\u00edch, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thao t\u00e1c \u1ea5n ph\u00edm qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:<\/strong>&nbsp;\u1ea4n ph\u00edm bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng micro<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2:<\/strong>&nbsp;N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd hi\u1ec7n pop up \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng,&nbsp;<strong>\u1ea5n OK<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3:<\/strong>&nbsp;\u00c2n ph\u00edm bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng micro, n\u00f3i t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a mu\u1ed1n xem<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4:<\/strong>&nbsp;B\u1ed9 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 